content: Thanks. Just to clarify, after I fill out the form and take the quiz, and then get contacted by a mod and receive the TTW link, then it's another 24-48 hours?
I guess I thought once i received the TTW link, that I'd been added.
So we're humans. We don't have an way to add an scale to win link. You would need to tell us when you've done that.
It should take 24-48 hours for us to send you an direct message though since we have so many.
sorry I was saying TTW, it's STW. Thanks
